      "solution": "<div><h4 style='color: #f87171; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 16px; font-size: 1.125rem;'>A) INCORRECT:</h4>A <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Dl01_T&anker=Za22be401f870f4a4d3a5049870aa9425\" data-learningcard-id=\"Dl01_T\" data-anker=\"Za22be401f870f4a4d3a5049870aa9425\" data-section-id=\"VxXGvZ0\" data-sememe-id=\"PjdW0J0\">thumb spica splint</a> is used for <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=T3063f&anker=Z614665fe523af7333fad58e1e2ab8f0f\" data-learningcard-id=\"T3063f\" data-anker=\"Z614665fe523af7333fad58e1e2ab8f0f\">fractures</a> of the thumb and wrist, not <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=T3063f&anker=Z614665fe523af7333fad58e1e2ab8f0f\" data-learningcard-id=\"T3063f\" data-anker=\"Z614665fe523af7333fad58e1e2ab8f0f\">fractures</a> of the fifth <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=3p0S6S&anker=Z27a865e4ece090e62885a6bec2d2848f\" data-learningcard-id=\"3p0S6S\" data-anker=\"Z27a865e4ece090e62885a6bec2d2848f\" data-section-id=\"swct4e0\" data-sememe-id=\"fYXko9\">metacarpal</a>.</div><div><h4 style='color: #34d399; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 16px; font-size: 1.125rem;'>B) CORRECT:</h4>An <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Dl01_T&anker=Z99853f4b037c5f58916fbe631f0e775b\" data-learningcard-id=\"Dl01_T\" data-anker=\"Z99853f4b037c5f58916fbe631f0e775b\" data-section-id=\"VxXGvZ0\" data-sememe-id=\"Dfd1o60\">ulnar gutter splint</a> is the appropriate <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Dl01_T&anker=Z93de3e78c53617451068745e69433cd3\" data-learningcard-id=\"Dl01_T\" data-anker=\"Z93de3e78c53617451068745e69433cd3\" data-section-id=\"gsWF850\" data-sememe-id=\"aTdQ660\">immobilization</a> technique for a <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=T3063f&anker=Z614665fe523af7333fad58e1e2ab8f0f\" data-learningcard-id=\"T3063f\" data-anker=\"Z614665fe523af7333fad58e1e2ab8f0f\">fracture</a> of the fifth <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=3p0S6S&anker=Z27a865e4ece090e62885a6bec2d2848f\" data-learningcard-id=\"3p0S6S\" data-anker=\"Z27a865e4ece090e62885a6bec2d2848f\" data-section-id=\"swct4e0\" data-sememe-id=\"fYXko9\">metacarpal</a>.</div><div><h4 style='color: #f87171; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 16px; font-size: 1.125rem;'>C) INCORRECT:</h4>A <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Dl01_T&anker=Z80700d0adbadd455ff75407de5f7921d\" data-learningcard-id=\"Dl01_T\" data-anker=\"Z80700d0adbadd455ff75407de5f7921d\" data-section-id=\"VxXGvZ0\" data-sememe-id=\"4jd30J0\">sugar tong forearm splint</a> is used for <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=TF06h3&anker=Z3095cf308256bc83c05476d4d6045efd\" data-learningcard-id=\"TF06h3\" data-anker=\"Z3095cf308256bc83c05476d4d6045efd\">forearm fractures</a>, not <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=T3063f&anker=Z614665fe523af7333fad58e1e2ab8f0f\" data-learningcard-id=\"T3063f\" data-anker=\"Z614665fe523af7333fad58e1e2ab8f0f\">fractures</a> of the fifth <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=3p0S6S&anker=Z27a865e4ece090e62885a6bec2d2848f\" data-learningcard-id=\"3p0S6S\" data-anker=\"Z27a865e4ece090e62885a6bec2d2848f\" data-section-id=\"swct4e0\" data-sememe-id=\"fYXko9\">metacarpal</a>.</div><div><h4 style='color: #f87171; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 16px; font-size: 1.125rem;'>D) INCORRECT:</h4>A <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Dl01_T&anker=Z2f99ea0429ed1d0f55fcba28496e5701\" data-learningcard-id=\"Dl01_T\" data-anker=\"Z2f99ea0429ed1d0f55fcba28496e5701\" data-section-id=\"VxXGvZ0\" data-sememe-id=\"kjdm0J0\">coaptation splint</a> is a U-shaped <span data-sememe-id=\"3hVSd80\">splint</span> used for <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=j30_Rf&anker=Zdc087940a1623b94c7b92fd6132a66d8\" data-learningcard-id=\"j30_Rf\" data-anker=\"Zdc087940a1623b94c7b92fd6132a66d8\" data-section-id=\"0OaeIk\">humeral shaft fractures</a> and other upper arm injuries, not <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=T3063f&anker=Z614665fe523af7333fad58e1e2ab8f0f\" data-learningcard-id=\"T3063f\" data-anker=\"Z614665fe523af7333fad58e1e2ab8f0f\">fractures</a> of the fifth <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=3p0S6S&anker=Z27a865e4ece090e62885a6bec2d2848f\" data-learningcard-id=\"3p0S6S\" data-anker=\"Z27a865e4ece090e62885a6bec2d2848f\" data-section-id=\"swct4e0\" data-sememe-id=\"fYXko9\">metacarpal</a>.</div><div><h4 style='color: #f87171; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 16px; font-size: 1.125rem;'>E) INCORRECT:</h4>A <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Dl01_T&anker=Z09f75b964527c439989e74e34ea9ce64\" data-learningcard-id=\"Dl01_T\" data-anker=\"Z09f75b964527c439989e74e34ea9ce64\" data-section-id=\"VxXGvZ0\" data-sememe-id=\"wfdho60\">radial gutter splint</a> is used for <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=T3063f&anker=Z614665fe523af7333fad58e1e2ab8f0f\" data-learningcard-id=\"T3063f\" data-anker=\"Z614665fe523af7333fad58e1e2ab8f0f\">fractures</a> of the second and third <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=3p0S6S&anker=Z27a865e4ece090e62885a6bec2d2848f\" data-learningcard-id=\"3p0S6S\" data-anker=\"Z27a865e4ece090e62885a6bec2d2848f\" data-section-id=\"swct4e0\" data-sememe-id=\"fYXko9\">metacarpal</a>, not the fifth <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=3p0S6S&anker=Z27a865e4ece090e62885a6bec2d2848f\" data-learningcard-id=\"3p0S6S\" data-anker=\"Z27a865e4ece090e62885a6bec2d2848f\" data-section-id=\"swct4e0\" data-sememe-id=\"fYXko9\">metacarpal</a>.</div>",
